item.title: [HIVE-21582] Prefix msck configs with metastore
item.description: HIVE-20707 moved msck configs to metastore but the configs are not prefixed with "metastore". Will be good to prefix it with "metastore" for consistency with other configs.

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are not closed can be reopened.
